<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="fan-n">fan <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fæn/    美 /fæn/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>扇子；风扇：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an electric fan
电扇</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(运动、电影等的) 狂热爱好者；迷：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'm a football fan and like watching football games.
我是个足球迷，喜欢观看足球比赛。</p><footer>2008 浙江</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The boy is <strong>a big fan of</strong> Marvel movies.
那个男孩是漫威电影的狂热粉丝。</p></div></div>